Please, you guys should just get up.
This is informal.

00:02:37.920 --> 00:02:40.890
Yes.
Chris, Jeremy, Robert, Michael, Richard.

00:02:40.890 --> 00:02:47.620
Did I miss anybody?
We've had a couple.

