We just -- as artists and people involved

00:26:42.370 --> 00:26:44.250
with origami -- we just want to thank Vanessa
for the wonderful story that she's told about

00:26:44.250 --> 00:26:53.100
this group of people.
Going back several years, a lot of these people

00:26:53.100 --> 00:26:59.040
were folding in relative isolation.
There were small conventions and a few publications.

00:26:59.040 --> 00:27:01.800
And when Michael and I opened the Origamido
Studio in 1996, I searched the word "origami"

00:27:01.800 --> 00:27:09.559
